title: Red Hot Chili Peppers - Live in Milan 2006 (mp3 @320kbps)
description:
This is originally sold as a live Blu-Ray / DVD, but I loved the concert and quality so much I decided to rip the audio, split the tracks up, and convert to mp3 so I could have it in my music collection as well. I especially love the Stadium Arcadium songs live versions. This is Live in Milan, Italy from the Stadium Arcadium tour on April 29, 2006. If you're a fan of Live at Slane Castle or Hyde Park I definitely suggest checking this out!
